(67324, 160205, 6123, 3, 'It''s All Gone', '讓大家久等一年了，在此送上新歌 - It''s All Gone！\n\n畢業季節，\n你，有想起誰嗎?\n一個以前如糖痴豆的best friend? \n一班一齊經歷一切考試測驗的同學?\n\n...還是後悔沒有說一些東西?\n\n感謝小彤的編曲還有阿火的鼓，為這歌添上色彩。\n給你的。給你們的\nIt''s All Gone\n\nText by Electone\n31/5/2013', '2013-08-12 00:00:00', 2013, 11, 0, 6, 'Ch.3 It’s All Gone\n作曲 / 作詞 / 監製：陳蔚琦 @ Electone Music \n編曲：賴映彤 @ groovision\n\nKeyboard & Programming by 賴映彤 @ groovision\nAll guitars by 陳蔚琦 @ Electone Music \nDrums by Fire Tse\nVocal produced by 譚天樂\nMixed by 宋嘉恆\nOP: Electone Music Limited 2013\n\nDuring class at noon\nYou were the one who woke me up\nSmiled like sun at noon\nThat’s what I remember at my last day in high school\n\n*And I\nMiss the days when we’re messing around\nHow we yelled and screamed at the playground\nBut now\n\nIt’s all gone \nJust hope that nothing goes wrong\nPlease don’t forget me \nAfter all these years yeah\nCause’ I \nCause’ I wrote you a song\nI wrote you a song*\n\nNo more notes and books\nBut Struggle starts to make me lose my hope\nI wonder if there’s any cloak\nFly me back to the past I don’t wanna grow\n\nRepeat *\n\nBack to the day when we wore the graduation gown\nWe cried a lot, cried a lot at the crowd\nOh please back up the time, the time we gathered around\nCause it’s undone\n\nIt’s all gone \nJust hope that nothing goes wrong\nPlease don’t forget me \nAfter all these years yeah\nCause’ I\n\nCause’ I wrote you a song \nJust hope that nothing goes wrong\nPlease don’t forget me\nAfter all these years yeah\nCause’ I wrote you a song (play back, flash back)\nWrote you a song, da dalala dalala la (play back, yeah-e-yeah)\nNa-who-whoa (play back, flash back, play back)\nIt’s all gone', '', 208, '', '陳蔚琦 @ Electone Music', '陳蔚琦 @ Electone Music', '陳蔚琦 @ Electone Music', 'Electone Music Limited (HK)', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-10-18 13:29:54', '2015-03-12 14:02:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
